HEADWORD: Acetimeter
<hw>Ac`e*tim"e*ter</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>acetum</ets> vinegar + <ets>-meter</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>ac⟦eacute⟧tim⟦egrave⟧tre</ets>.]</ety> <def>An instrument for
